author: jerenkrantz
msg: Add -m option to mod-mbox-util to dump the mbox message-id cache
(replaces the load_msgid tool which was never updated when this was introduced.)

author: gangolli
msg: Fix/improvements for ROL-1192 onto roller_3.0 branch. Introduce statically configurable mechanism for interoperating with buggy WeblogUpdates.ping variants.  Implement "noname" ping variant (which omits the name parameter from the ping) in order to support pings to IceRocket.   Be resilient to responses of the wrong type (also for IceRocket).  Add IceRocket to default initial common targets.
